item.title: Student Leaders from Jogulamba Gadwal Head to Telangana Student Conference in Hyderabad
item.description:
<![CDATA[-Advertisement-
A group of student leaders from Bharat Rashtra Samithi Vidyarthi (BRSV) in Jogulamba Gadwal district traveled to Hyderabad for the BRSV State-Level Telangana Student Conference at VNR Gardens, Mallapur, Uppal today.
Led by Kurva Pallayya, the BRSV Jogulamba Gadwal District Coordinator, these energetic students set off early to join this important event. The conference will focus on student issues, leadership, and the future of the student organization.
